summary: This is the final version of the AA Dwarven bow, including matching quiver.
descriptionHtml:
This is the final version of the AA Dwarven bow, including matching quiver.

Each finish from here on out will be color-matched and schemed the same as these.

Enjoy the file, and endorse if you please.

This file is provided as-is to do with however the downloader wishes.
